Mutane fiye da miliyan 20 sun kalli yadda Brett Kavanaugh ya ji
Mutane sama da miliyan 20 sun kalli shaidar da aka gabatar a ranar Alhamis ta dan takarar Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh da kuma matar da ta zarge shi da cin zarafin jima'i da ake zargin ya faru a shekarun 1980, Christine Blasey Ford, a tashoshin talabijin shida.
A halin yanzu, rikice-rikicen siyasa ya ci gaba, tare da masu watsa shirye-shirye na katse shirye-shiryen yau da kullum don juyin juya halin ranar Juma'a na minti na ƙarshe: yarjejeniya da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya tsara don FBI ta gudanar da bincike na mako guda game da zargin.
Ford ta gaya wa Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattawa cewa ta tabbata da kashi 100 cikin 100 cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata barawo da maye kuma ya yi kokarin cire tufafinta a wani biki na makarantar sakandare.
Kavanaugh, a cikin shaidar sha'awarsa, ya ce ya tabbata 100% cewa ba a faru ba.
Mai yiwuwa fiye da mutane miliyan 20.4 da Nielsen ta ruwaito a ranar Juma'a sun kalli shi.
Kamfanin yana ƙidaya yawan masu kallo a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a samu kididdigar nan take ba ga sauran cibiyoyin sadarwa da suka nuna shi, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Kuma Nielsen yawanci yana da matsala wajen auna mutanen da suke kallo a ofisoshin.
Don sanya wannan a cikin hangen nesa, wannan shine girman masu sauraro kamar na wasan kwallon kafa na wasan kwaikwayo ko Academy Awards.
Fox News Channel, wanda masu gabatar da ra'ayoyin su sun goyi bayan karbar Kavanaugh, ya jagoranci dukkan hanyoyin sadarwa tare da matsakaicin masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a lokacin sauraron ranar, in ji Nielsen.
ABC ta kasance na biyu tare da masu kallo miliyan 3.26 .
CBS na da miliyan 3,1, NBC na da miliyan 2,94, MSNBC na da miliyan 2,89 kuma CNN na da miliyan 2,52, in ji Nielsen.
Ƙari ga haka, bayan taron, an ci gaba da nuna sha'awa sosai.
Flake shi ne babban mutum a wasan kwaikwayo na Juma'a.
Bayan da ofishin dan jam'iyyar Republican mai matsakaici ya fitar da wata sanarwa cewa zai kada kuri'a a madadin Kavanaugh, an kama shi a gaban kyamarorin CNN da CBS a safiyar Juma'a ana ihu da shi ta hanyar masu zanga-zanga yayin da yake kokarin hawa lif zuwa sauraron Kwamitin Shari'a.
Ya tsaya yana kallon ƙasa na minti da dama yayin da ake tsauta masa, a talabijin a kai a kai a CNN.
Wata mata ta ce: "Ina tsaye a gabanka".
"Kuna tsammanin yana gaya wa ƙasar gaskiya ne?
An gaya masa, "kana da iko lokacin da mata da yawa ba su da iko. ""
Flake ya ce ofishinsa ya fitar da wata sanarwa kuma ya ce, kafin a rufe lif din, zai kara da cewa a taron kwamitin.
Kabila da kuma watsa shirye-shiryen watsa shirye-shirye duk suna watsa shirye-shiryen kai tsaye bayan sa'o'i, lokacin da Kwamitin Shari'a ya kamata ya kada kuri'a don gabatar da takarar Kavanaugh zuwa majalisar dattijai don jefa kuri'a.
Amma Flake ya ce zai yi hakan ne kawai da sanin cewa FBI za ta duba zargin da ake yi wa dan takarar a mako mai zuwa, wanda 'yan Democrat na ƙaramin rinjaye ke kira.
Flake ya rinjayi shi a wani ɓangare ta hanyar tattaunawa da abokinsa, Sanata Democrat Chris Coons.
Bayan tattaunawa da Coons da wasu Sanatoci bayan haka, Flake ya yanke shawararsa.
Zaɓin Flake yana da iko, domin a bayyane yake 'yan Republican ba za su sami kuri'un da za su amince da Kavanaugh ba tare da binciken ba.
