Kanye West: Rapper ya canza sunansa zuwa Ye
Rapper Kanye West yana canza sunansa zuwa Ye.
A sanar da canjin a shafinsa na Twitter a ranar Asabar, ya rubuta: "Sanarwar da aka sani da Kanye West".
West, 41, ya kasance mai suna Ye na wani lokaci kuma ya yi amfani da sunan a matsayin taken don kundi na takwas, wanda aka saki a watan Yuni.
Canjin ya zo ne kafin ya bayyana a ranar Asabar da dare, inda ake sa ran zai kaddamar da sabon kundin Yandhi.
Ya maye gurbin mawaƙa Ariana Grande a cikin wasan kwaikwayon wanda ya soke saboda "la'akari da motsin rai", in ji mai kirkirar wasan kwaikwayon.
Baya ga kasancewa gajarta sunan sana'arsa na yanzu, West ya riga ya ce kalmar tana da ma'ana ta addini a gare shi.
West ya ce: "Na yi imani cewa 'ya' ne kalmar da aka fi amfani da ita a cikin Littafi Mai Tsarki, kuma a cikin Littafi Mai Tsarki tana nufin 'ku,'" a farkon wannan shekara, yana tattauna taken kundin sa da mai gabatar da rediyo Big Boy.
"Saboda haka ni ne kai, ni ne mu, mu ne.
Daga Kanye, wanda ke nufin wanda ya kasance shi kaɗai, zuwa Ye - kawai yana nuna mana nagarta, mu mugunta, mu rikice, komai.
Wannan kundin ya fi nuna ko wane ne mu".
Yana daya daga cikin shahararrun rappers da suka canza sunayensu.
Sean Combs an san shi da sunan Puff Daddy, P. Diddy ko Diddy, amma a wannan shekara ya sanar da fifiko ga sunayen Love da Brother Love.
Wani tsohon abokin aikin West, JAY-Z, ya yi aiki tare da ko ba tare da alamar rubutu da manyan haruffa ba.
