Lokacin Taron Trump na West Virginia, Tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara taron neman zabe a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan ne na farko daga cikin tarurrukan da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Tare da zaben tabbatarwa a jiransa don ya zaɓa don cika wurin da Kotun Koli ta buɗe, Trump yana nufin gina goyon baya ga zaɓen tsakiyar lokaci mai zuwa tunda 'yan Republican suna cikin haɗarin rasa ikon Majalisar lokacin da aka jefa kuri'u a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump na West Virginia yake yau da dare kuma yaya za ku kalli layi?
An shirya taron Trump na Wheeling, West Virginia don karfe 7 na yamma ET a yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Kuna iya kallon taron Trump na West Virginia a kan layi a ƙasa ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen kai tsaye akan YouTube.
Ana sa ran Trump zai yi magana a wannan makon a sauraron dan takarar Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya zama mai rikitarwa a kan zargin lalata ta jima'i tare da sa ran za a dakatar da zaben Majalisar Dattawa har zuwa mako guda yayin da FBI ke bincike.
Amma babban burin wannan gangamin gangami shine taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar zaben Nuwamba su samu karfafawa.
Saboda haka, yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump ya ce wadannan tarurruka guda biyar a mako mai zuwa suna nufin "karfafa masu sa kai da magoya baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin kare da fadada rinjayen da suke da su a Majalisar Dattawa da Majalisar Wakilai", a cewar Reuters.
"Sarrafawa da majalisar dokoki na da matukar muhimmanci ga tsarinsa cewa shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama kamar yadda zai yiwu yayin da muke shiga cikin lokacin yakin neman zabe", in ji wani mai magana da yawun yakin neman zaben Trump wanda ya ki bayyana sunansa ga Reuters.
An shirya a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, taron na yau zai iya kawo magoya baya daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma jawo rahoto daga kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh", a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
Asabar za ta zama karo na biyu a watan da ya gabata da Trump ya ziyarci West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe fiye da maki 40 a shekarar 2016.
Trump na kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai ta Jam'iyyar Republican ta West Virginia Patrick Morrisey, wanda ya rage a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya zo ya yi kokarin ba shi ci gaba a zaben", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
