Maganarsa ta jawo hankalin masu sauraro aƙalla sau biyu kuma membobin SNL sun bayyana suna jin kunya, Variety ta ruwaito, tare da wani mutum a wurin ya gaya wa wallafe-wallafen: "Dukan ɗakin ya yi shiru".
An kawo West a matsayin maye gurbin mawaƙa Ariana Grande, wanda tsohon saurayinsa, rapper Mac Miller ya mutu 'yan kwanaki da suka wuce.
