Tauraruwar wasan sarauta Kit Harington ta yi nasara a cikin namiji mai guba
Kit Harington sananne ne saboda rawar da yake takawa kamar Jon Snow a cikin wasan kwaikwayo na wasan kwaikwayo na HBO Game of Thrones .
Amma dan wasan mai shekara 31, ya yi watsi da irin wannan hali na jarumin macho, yana cewa irin waɗannan rawar da ake yi a allon suna nufin matasa sukan ji cewa dole ne su kasance masu wuya don a girmama su.
A wata hira da ya yi da jaridar The Sunday Times Culture, Kit ya ce ya yi imanin cewa 'wani abu ya faru ba daidai ba' kuma ya yi tambaya game da yadda za a magance matsalar namiji mai guba a zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri ta Game of Thrones co-star Rose Leslie, kuma 31, ya yarda yana jin 'da gaske' game da magance batun.
Ya ce: 'Na ji da kaina, sosai, a wannan lokacin - ina muka yi kuskure game da namiji?
'Me muka koya wa maza sa'ad da suke girma, game da matsalar da muke gani yanzu?'
Kit ya yi imanin cewa talabijin na iya zama wani ɓangare mai alhakin karuwar namiji mai guba godiya ga halayensa na namiji.
Ya ci gaba: 'Mece ce ta halitta da kuma abin da ake koyarwa?
Abin da ake koyarwa a talabijin, da kuma a tituna, da ke sa yara maza su ji cewa dole ne su kasance wannan bangare na kasancewa mutum?
Ina ganin wannan na daga cikin manyan tambayoyi a zamaninmu - ta yaya za mu canza wannan?
Domin a fili wani abu ya faru da matasa.'
A cikin hira ya kuma yarda cewa ba zai yi wani wasa na Game of Thrones prequels ko sequels lokacin da jerin ya zo karshen gaba rani, yana cewa shi ne 'yi da fagen fama da dawakai.'
Daga watan Nuwamba Kit zai taka rawa a cikin sake farfadowar Sam Shepard ta Gaskiya West wanda shine labarin wani mai shirya fim da ɗan'uwansa, wanda yake fashi.
A kwanan nan, actor ya bayyana cewa yana ganin saduwa da matarsa Rose shine mafi kyawun abu da zai fito daga Game of Thrones.
Ya ce: 'Na sadu da matata a wannan wasan kwaikwayon, don haka ta wannan hanyar na sami iyalina na gaba, da rayuwata daga nan gaba.
Rose ya taka leda Ygritte, ƙaunar ƙaunar mutumi na Kit Jon Snow, a cikin jerin abubuwan da suka lashe kyautar Emmy.
Ma'auratan sun yi aure a watan Yuni 2018 a kan tushen gidan Leslie a Scotland.
HIV/AIDS: China ta ba da rahoton karuwar kashi 14% na sababbin cututtuka
Kasar Sin ta sanar da cewa yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da Aids ya karu da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Jami'an lafiya sun ce mutane fiye da 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a kasar.
An samu sabbin mutane 40,000 a cikin kwata na biyu na shekarar 2018 kadai.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka sun gudana ne ta hanyar jima'i, kuma hakan ya nuna cewa an canja yanayin da aka yi a dā.
A wasu wurare a ƙasar Sin, an yi amfani da jini don a yi wa mutane maganin HIV.
Amma an rage yawan mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar zuwa kusan sifili, kamar yadda jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin suka ce a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Amma, a shekara guda, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da Aids a ƙasar Sin ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
Yada HIV ta hanyar jima'i abu ne mai tsanani a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An dakatar da cin zarafin 'yan luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma ana cewa nuna bambanci ga LGBTs ya zama ruwan dare.
Saboda ra'ayin da kasar take da shi, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin 100 na maza da suke yin jima'i da maza za su auri mata a ƙarshe.
Yawancin cututtuka na kamuwa da cuta sun fito ne daga rashin kariya ta jima'i a cikin waɗannan dangantaka.
Tun shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samun magani ga kowa don cutar HIV a matsayin wani ɓangare na ƙoƙarin magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta ma'aikatan sun yi watsi da bayanan 'yan majalisar dokoki na GOP, ta yi ikirarin 'ƙaryaci mai haɗari' da 'ka'idojin shiririta'
Wakilin Amurka Maxine Waters a ranar Asabar ta yi Allah wadai da zargin da ake yi cewa wani memba na ma'aikatanta ya sanya bayanan sirri na sanatocin Amurka uku na Jam'iyyar Republican a shafukan Wikipedia na 'yan majalisa.
'Yan Democrat na Los Angeles sun ce masana da shafukan yanar gizo na "daidaici" ne ke yin amfani da wannan ikirarin.
Waters ya ce a wani bayani a shafinsa na Twitter: "Ƙarya, ƙarya, da kuma ƙara ƙyama".
Rahotanni sun ce bayanan da aka fitar sun hada da adiresoshin gida da lambobin waya na Sanarwar Amurka Lindsey Graham na South Carolina, da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, duka daga Utah.
Bayanan sun bayyana a yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis, wanda wani ba a san shi ba ya sanya a kan Capitol Hill yayin sauraron majalisar dattijai game da zargin lalata da ake yi wa dan takarar Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh.
Wannan sanarwa ta fito ne bayan da Sanatoci uku suka yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Shafuka masu ra'ayin mazan jiya kamar su Gateway Pundit da RedState sun ruwaito cewa adireshin IP wanda ya gano asalin sakonnin ya danganta da ofishin Waters kuma ya fitar da bayanan wani memba na ma'aikatan Waters, Hill ta ruwaito.
Waters ya ci gaba da cewa, "Wannan zargin da ba shi da tushe ƙarya ne kuma ƙarya ce".
"Wani ma'aikacina - wanda aka ɓata sunansa da kuma bayanansa na sirri da kuma amincinsa saboda waɗannan zarge-zargen na ƙarya - ba shi da alhakin wannan ɓoyewar.
Wannan zargin da ba shi da tushe ƙarya ce gaba ɗaya".
Sanarwar Waters ta jawo karambanin zargi a yanar gizo, ciki har da daga tsohon sakataren yada labarai na fadar White House Ari Fleischer.
Fleischer ya rubuta: "Wannan ƙin yarda da abin da na faɗa yana da ban haushi.
"Wannan ya nuna cewa ba ta da ƙarfin hali ta zama 'yar majalisa.
Idan aka zargi wani da wani abu da bai yi ba, kada ka yi fushi.
Ba za su yi rashin biyayya ba.
Kada su yi tambaya game da dalilin da ya sa ake tuhumarsu.
Dole ne su kasance da kwanciyar hankali".
Fleischer ya bayyana yana kwatanta yadda Waters ya amsa da sukar 'yan Democrat ga Alkalin Kavanaugh, wanda masu sukar suka zargi da yin fushi sosai a lokacin sauraron Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar jam'iyyar Republican da ke neman tsige Waters a zaben tsakiyar lokaci, ya kuma bayyana tunaninsa a shafin Twitter.
Ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa: "Babban idan gaskiya ne.
A cikin sanarwar ta, Waters ta ce ofishinta ya sanar da " hukumomi da hukumomin da suka dace da wadannan ikirarin zamba.
Ta ci gaba da cewa: "Za mu tabbata cewa an fallasa masu aikata laifin, kuma za a ɗauke su da alhakin dukan ayyukan da suke yi da za su iya hallaka da kuma yin haɗari ga dukan ma'aikatanmu".
Johnny English ya sake yin yaƙi sake dubawa - Rowan Atkinson mai ƙarancin iko ya yi wa 'yan leƙen asiri
A yanzu al'ada ce a nemi ma'anar Brexit a kowane sabon fim da ke da yanayin Burtaniya kuma hakan ya zama kamar ya shafi wannan farfadowar wasan kwaikwayo na Johnny English - wanda ya fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma ya sake farfadowa a 2011 tare da Johnny English Reborn.
Shin, yin baƙar magana game da kanmu game da yadda muke da tsabta zai zama sabuwar damar fitarwa ga al'ummar?
A kowane hali, Johnny English mai ido mai haske, marar iya aiki da fuskar roba ya sake sabunta lasisinsa na yin lalata da abubuwa a karo na biyu - wannan sunan yana nuna fiye da kowane abu cewa shi babban zane ne na zane-zane da aka tsara don yankunan da ba Turanci ba.
Hakika shi ne wakili mai zaman kansa wanda duk da irin wannan tunanin da yake yi na yin amfani da shi don ya saukaka sha'awa, ya samu wani ɗan Clouseau, da wani ɗan Mr Bean da kuma wani ɗan ɗan ƙaramin ɗan ƙaramin mutumin da ya ba da wata sanarwa ɗaya ga taken "Wakar Wuta ta Wuta" a bikin buɗe gasar Olympics ta London 2012.
An kuma kafa shi ne a asali a kan matafiyi da kuma mutum na duniya na asiri Atkinson wanda ya taba taka leda a yanzu manta Barclaycard TV tallace-tallace, barin rikici a cikinsa.
Akwai lokaci ɗaya ko biyu masu kyau a wannan sabon tafiyar JE.
Ina son Johnny English da yake zuwa jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu yana sanye da rigar ƙarni na dā kuma ƙusa mai juyawa suna ta daɗaɗaɗa a kan kwalkwali.
Kyautar Atkinson ga wasan kwaikwayo na jiki tana kan gani, amma ban dariya yana jin rashin ƙarfi da rashin amfani, musamman ma yayin da "m" fina-finai kamar 007 da Mission Impossible kansu yanzu suna ba da wasan kwaikwayo a matsayin kayan aiki.
Abin dariya yana jin kamar an yi wa yara maimakon manya, kuma a gare ni Johnny English na rashin jin dadi ba su da kwarewa da kuma mayar da hankali kamar Atkinson na silent-movies gags a cikin mutum Bean.
Yanzu dai, abin da ya fi muhimmanci a yau shi ne cewa Birtaniya tana cikin matsala.
Wani dan gwanin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin hanyar sadarwar leken asiri ta yanar gizo ta Burtaniya, yana bayyana ainihin dukkan jami'an Burtaniya a filin, wanda ya ba da mamaki ga jami'in da ke aiki - abin takaici ne ga Kevin Eldon.
Wannan ita ce ƙarancin ƙura ga firaministan da yake da girman kai da kuma rashin ƙarfi, wanda ya riga ya sha wahala daga cikakken rikici na rashin shahararren siyasa: Emma Thompson ta yi iyakar ƙoƙarinta tare da wannan halin na Teresa-May amma babu wani abu mai yawa a cikin rubutun da za a yi aiki da shi.
Masu ba ta shawara na leken asirin sun sanar da ita cewa tun da aka yi wa kowane ɗan leken asiri da ke aiki barazana, dole ne ta fitar da wani daga ritaya.
Kuma wannan yana nufin yin lalata da Johnny English kansa, yanzu yana aiki a matsayin malamin makaranta a wani wuri mai kyau, amma yana ba da darasi na musamman game da yadda za a zama jami'in ɓoye: wasu kyawawan gags a nan, kamar yadda Turanci ke ba da makarantar makarantar leken asiri na Rock.
An kai English zuwa Whitehall don ganawar gaggawa kuma ya sake haɗuwa da tsohon abokin aikinsa mai haƙuri Bough, wanda Ben Miller ya sake buga.
Bough yanzu ya yi aure, ya yi aure ga kwamandan jirgin ruwa, wani rawar da ake yi da 'yan wasan hockey, inda Vicki Pepperdine ta yi rashin hankali.
Don haka Batman da Robin na yin mummunan kuskure a cikin Sirrin Maɗaukaki sun dawo cikin aiki, suna haɗuwa da kyakkyawan matar Olga Kurylenko, Ophelia Bulletova.
A halin yanzu, firaministan na fada cikin hatsari a cikin sihiri na mai karfin fasaha wanda ya ce zai iya magance matsalolin kwamfuta na Birtaniya: Jason Volta mai ban tsoro, wanda Jake Lacy ya buga.
Turanci da Bough sun fara odyssey na masu ban dariya: sun yi kama da masu hidima, sun ƙone gidan cin abinci na Faransa mai haske; sun haifar da rikici suna fashin kansu a cikin jirgin ruwan luxury na Volta; kuma Turanci ya haifar da lalataccen rikici yayin da yake ƙoƙarin amfani da belun kunne na Virtual Reality don sanin kansa da ciki na gidan Volta.
Hakika an dakatar da duk abubuwan da aka yi domin wannan fim na karshe, amma duk da cewa yana da kyau kuma yana da ƙarfi, akwai wasu shirye-shiryen talabijin na yara game da dukan abu.
Abu ne mai matsakaici.
Kuma kamar sauran fina-finai na Johnny English ba zan iya taimakawa ba tunani: Shin masana'antar fim ta Burtaniya ba za ta iya ba Rowan Atkinson rawar da ta yi adalci ga baiwarsa ba?
Ma'aikatan Labour sun musanta cewa suna tsara shirin da zai sa 'yan Birtaniya su yi aiki kwana hudu a mako amma su samu albashi na kwanaki biyar
Jam'iyyar Labour ta Jeremy Corbyn za ta yi la'akari da shirin da zai sa Britaniyawa su yi aiki na kwana hudu a mako - amma za a biya su biyar.
An ruwaito cewa jam'iyyar na son shugabannin kamfanoni su ba da kuɗin da aka samu ta hanyar juyin juya halin fasaha na wucin gadi (AI) ga ma'aikata ta hanyar ba su karin ranar hutu.
Hakan zai sa ma'aikata su yi kwana uku a ƙarshen mako, amma su riƙa karɓar albashin da suka samu.
Majiyoyi sun ce wannan ra'ayin zai "dace" da tsarin tattalin arzikin jam'iyyar kuma yana shirin karkatar da kasar zuwa ga ma'aikata.
Ma'aikatan kungiyar kwadago sun amince da sauya zuwa mako na kwana hudu a matsayin hanya ga ma'aikata su yi amfani da tattalin arzikin da ke canjawa.
Wani babban majiya a jam'iyyar Labour ya shaida wa jaridar Sunday Times: "Ana sa ran za a sanar da sake duba manufofin kafin karshen shekara.
"Ba zai faru ba amma sati na aiki na kwana hudu yana da burin da ya dace da tsarin jam'iyyar na sake daidaita tattalin arziki a cikin fa'idar ma'aikaci da kuma tsarin masana'antu na jam'iyyar".
Jam'iyyar Labour ba zata kasance ta farko da za ta amince da irin wannan ra'ayin ba, tare da Jam'iyyar Green ta yi alkawarin yin aiki na kwanaki hudu a lokacin yakin neman zaben ta shekara ta 2017.
Duk da haka, a halin yanzu jam'iyyar Labour ba ta amince da wannan burin ba.
Wani kakakin jam'iyyar Labour ya ce: "Matsalolin aiki na kwana hudu ba siyasa ba ce kuma jam'iyyar ba ta yin la'akari da shi ba".
Shadow Chancellor John McDonnell ya yi amfani da taron Labour na makon da ya gabata don ya bayyana hangen nesa na juyin juya halin zamantakewa a tattalin arziki.
Mista McDonnell ya ce ya ƙuduri aniya ya dawo da iko daga "masu gudanarwa marasa fuska" da "masu cin riba" a kamfanonin amfani.
Shirin Shadow Chancellor na nufin ma'aikatan ruwa na yanzu ba za su iya dawo da duk hannun jari ba saboda gwamnatin Labour na iya yin 'ƙididdiga' bisa laifukan da ake ɗauka.
Ya kuma tabbatar da shirye-shiryen sanya ma'aikata a cikin kwamitocin kamfanoni da kuma ƙirƙirar Asusun Mallaka na Haɗuwa don ba da kashi 10 cikin dari na hannun jari na kamfanoni masu zaman kansu ga ma'aikata, waɗanda ke da aljihunan shekara-shekara har zuwa £ 500.
Lindsey Graham, John Kennedy gaya "60 Minutes" ko FBI ta bincike Kavanaugh zai iya canza su tunani
Binciken FBI kan zargin da aka yi wa Alkalin Brett Kavanaugh ya jinkirta zaben karshe kan nadin sa a Kotun Koli da akalla mako guda, kuma ya tayar da tambaya ko binciken ofishin zai iya rinjayar wasu 'yan majalisar Republican su janye goyon bayansu.
A wata hira da aka watsa a ranar Lahadi, wakilin "60 Minutes" Scott Pelley ya tambayi 'yan Republican Sen. John Kennedy da Lindsey Graham ko FBI za su iya gano wani abu da zai sa su canja ra'ayinsu.
Kennedy ya bayyana ya fi bude fuska fiye da abokin aikinsa daga South Carolina.
"Ina nufin, ba shakka", in ji Kennedy.
"Na ce na je sauraron, na ce, na yi magana da Alkali Kavanaugh.
Na kira shi bayan wannan ya faru, cewa zargin ya fito, ya ce, 'Shin, ka yi shi?'
Ya kasance da ƙuduri, da ƙuduri, da kuma rashin jituwa".
Amma, an yi wa Graham da'awar cewa ya yi zabe.
Ya ce: "Na yanke shawara game da Brett Kavanaugh kuma zai bukaci a yi masa zargi da karfi.
Graham ya kara da cewa, "Ba na san abin da ya faru, amma na san wannan: Brett ya musanta shi sosai", yana nufin Christine Blasey Ford.
"Kuma duk wanda ta kira ba zai iya tabbatar da shi ba.
Yana da shekaru 36.
Ba na ganin wani sabon abu da ya canja".
Mene ne Bikin 'Yan Adam na Duniya, kuma Shin Ya Yi Wani Abu don Ya Ƙarfafa Talauci?
A wannan Asabar New York za ta karbi bakuncin bikin Global Citizen, wani taron kiɗa na shekara-shekara wanda ke da ban sha'awa sosai na taurari da ke yin wasan kwaikwayo da kuma manufa mai ban sha'awa; kawo karshen talauci a duniya.
Yanzu a shekara ta bakwai, bikin Global Citizen zai ga dubban mutane suna zuwa babban Lawn na Central Park ba kawai don jin daɗin ayyukan kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, har ma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin burin taron na kawar da matsanancin talauci ta 2030.
Bikin Global Citizen, wanda aka bayyana a shekarar 2012, wani ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, kungiyar kare talauci ta duniya da ke fatan kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke yaki da ita.
Don a ba su tikitin kyauta don taron (sai dai idan kana son ka biya tikitin VIP), masu halartar taron suna bukatar su yi ayyuka da yawa, ko kuma su yi "aiki" kamar su aikin sa kai, aika saƙon imel zuwa ga shugaban duniya, yin kiran waya ko kuma wasu hanyoyi masu ma'ana don su taimaka wajen wayar da kan mutane game da burinsu na kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya Global Citizen ta yi nasara da shekaru 12 da suka rage don cimma burinta?
Shin ra'ayin bayar da kyauta ga mutane tare da wani kide kide na gaske ne don shawo kan mutane su nemi kira ga aiki, ko kuma wani hali ne na abin da ake kira "clicktivism" - mutane suna jin kamar suna yin canji na gaske ta hanyar sanya hannu kan wata takarda ta yanar gizo ko aikawa da tweet?
Tun daga shekarar 2011, Global Citizen ta ce ta yi rikodin fiye da miliyan 19 na "aiki" daga magoya bayanta, suna turawa ga manufofi daban-daban.
Ya ce wadannan ayyukan sun taimaka wajen ƙarfafa shugabannin duniya su sanar da alkawura da manufofi da suka kai dala biliyan 37 da za su shafi rayuwar mutane biliyan 2.25 zuwa 2030.
A farkon 2018, ƙungiyar ta ambaci alkawura 390 da sanarwar da suka fito daga ayyukanta, wanda aƙalla dala biliyan 10 tuni aka biya ko an tara kuɗi.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa kudaden da aka tabbatar sun yi tasiri kai tsaye a kan kusan mutane miliyan 649 a duniya.
Wasu daga cikin manyan alkawuran sun hada da The Power of Nutrition, haɗin gwiwar masu saka jari da masu aiwatarwa da ke Burtaniya da suka himmatu ga "taimaka yara su bunkasa zuwa cikakkiyar damar su", suna alƙawarin samar wa Rwanda dala miliyan 35 don taimakawa kawo karshen rashin abinci mai gina jiki a gundumar bayan sun karɓi fiye da 4,700 tweets daga Global Citizens.
"Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu bayarwa, gwamnatocin kasa, da kuma 'yan kasa na duniya kamar ku, za mu iya sanya rashin adalci na zamantakewar rashin abinci mai gina jiki a tarihin", jakadan The Power of Nutrition, Tracey Ullman ya shaida wa taron a lokacin wani taro na kai tsaye a London a watan Afrilu 2018.
Kungiyar ta kuma ce bayan an dauki ayyuka sama da 5,000 da suka kira Birtaniya ta inganta abinci mai gina jiki ga iyaye mata da yara, gwamnati ta sanar da kudade don wani shiri, Power of Nutrition, wanda zai kai ga mata da yara miliyan 5 da ke fama da abinci mai gina jiki.
A cikin amsar da aka yi wa ɗaya daga cikin tambayoyin da ake yawan yi a shafinsa na yanar gizo da ke tambayar "me ya sa kake ganin za mu iya kawar da matsanancin talauci?"
Wani ɗan ƙasa a duniya ya amsa: "Wannan zai zama hanya mai tsawo da wuya - a wasu lokatai za mu faɗi kuma mu kasa.
Amma, kamar manyan ƙungiyoyin kare hakkin bil adama da na yaki da wariyar launin fata da ke gabanmu, za mu yi nasara, domin muna da iko sosai tare.
Janet Jackson, The Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B, Janelle Monáe suna cikin wasu daga cikin ayyukan da ke yin aiki a taron na wannan shekara a New York, wanda Deborra-Lee Furness da Hugh Jackman za su shirya.
Amurka na iya amfani da Rundunar Sojan Ruwa don "tallace-tallace" don hana fitar da makamashin Rasha - Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida
Washington na iya "idan ya zama dole" ya yi amfani da Rundunar Sojan Ruwa don hana makamashin Rasha shiga kasuwannin, ciki har da a Gabas ta Tsakiya, Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka Ryan Zinke ya bayyana, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ya ruwaito.
Zinke ya yi ikirarin cewa shigar Rasha a Syria - musamman, inda take aiki a kan gayyatar gwamnati ta halal - wani uzuri ne don bincika sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
"Na yi imanin dalilin da ya sa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne domin suna son yin amfani da makamashi kamar yadda suke yi a gabashin Turai, kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
Kuma, a cewar jami'in, akwai hanyoyi da kuma hanyoyin da za a magance shi.
"Amurka tana da wannan ikon, tare da rundunarmu ta ruwa, don tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin ruwa suna buɗewa, kuma, idan ya cancanta, don toshewa, don tabbatar da cewa makamashi ba ya zuwa kasuwa", in ji shi.
Zinke yana magana ne ga mahalarta taron da kungiyar Consumer Energy Alliance ta shirya, kungiyar da ba ta da riba wacce ke kiran kanta "muryar mai amfani da makamashi" a Amurka.
Ya je ya kwatanta hanyoyin Washington na hulɗa da Rasha da Iran, yana lura cewa suna da tasiri iri ɗaya.
"Zaɓin tattalin arziki a kan Iran da Rasha shine, mafi ko ƙasa da haka, amfani da kuma maye gurbin man fetur", in ji shi, yayin da yake magana game da Rasha a matsayin "daya-daya-daya-daya-daya-daya-daya" tare da tattalin arziki da ya dogara da burbushin halittu.
Sanarwar ta zo ne a lokacin da gwamnatin Trump ta kasance a kan manufa ta kara fitar da iskar gas dinta zuwa Turai, ta maye gurbin Rasha, zabin da ya fi arha ga masu amfani da Turai.
Don haka, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da shugaban Amurka Donald Trump da kansa, suna kokarin rinjayar Jamus ta janye daga aikin bututun "Nord Stream 2" wanda a cewar Trump, ya sa Berlin ta zama "ƙasar" ta Moscow.
Moscow ta sake jaddada cewa bututun mai na Nord Stream 2 da zai kai dala biliyan 11, wanda za a ninka karfin bututun mai zuwa biliyan 110 na mita, shiri ne na tattalin arziki kawai.
Kremlin ya yi jayayya cewa hamayya mai tsanani da Washington ke yi wa aikin ta samo asali ne daga dalilai na tattalin arziki kuma misali ne na rashin adalci.
"Na yi imanin cewa muna da ra'ayin cewa makamashi ba zai iya zama kayan aiki don yin matsi ba kuma ya kamata masu amfani su iya zaɓar masu samar da kayayyaki", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha Aleksandr Novak bayan ganawa da Ministan Makamashi na Amurka Rick Perry a Moscow a watan Satumba.
Matsayin Amurka ya jawo martani daga Jamus, wadda ta sake tabbatar da sadaukar da kanta ga aikin.
Babban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus, Federation of German Industries (BDI), ta yi kira ga Amurka ta guje wa siyasar makamashi ta EU da kuma yarjejeniyar biyu tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
"Ina da babbar matsala idan wata ƙasa ta uku ta tsoma baki a cikin samar da makamashi", in ji Dieter Kempf, shugaban Tarayyar Masana'antu ta Jamus (BDI) bayan ganawar da aka yi kwanan nan tsakanin shugabar gwamnatin Jamus Angela Merkel da shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin.
Elizabeth Warren Za Ta Yi "Bincike Mai Girma" A Tserewa A Matsayin Shugaban Kasa A 2020, Sanata Na Massachusetts Ya Ce
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta Massachusetts ta ce a ranar Asabar za ta yi "duba sosai" a kan takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben tsakiyar lokaci.
A lokacin da take taron da ke garin Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ta tabbatar da cewa za ta yi tunanin yin takara.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace kuma hakan ya haɗa da mace a saman", in ji ta, a cewar The Hill.
"Bayan 6 ga Nuwamba, zan yi la'akari da yadda zan yi takarar shugaban kasa".
Warren ya yi magana game da Shugaba Donald Trump a lokacin majalisar dattijai, yana cewa yana "daukan wannan gundumar a cikin mummunan shugabanci.
"Ina damuwa har zuwa ƙasusuwana game da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokiradiyya", in ji ta.
Warren ta kasance mai gaskiya a cikin ta sukar Trump da kuma dan takararsa na Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh.
A wani sakon da ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter a ranar Juma'a, Warren ya ce "Tabbas muna bukatar binciken FBI kafin mu kada kuri'a".
Amma, wani bincike da aka yi a ranar Alhamis ya nuna cewa yawancin masu jefa kuri'a na Warren ba su yi tunanin cewa ta tsaya takara a shekarar 2020.
Kashi 58 cikin 100 na masu jefa kuri'a na Massachusetts sun ce bai kamata sanatan ya tsaya takara ba, a cewar binciken Cibiyar Nazarin Siyasa ta Jami'ar Suffolk / Boston Globe.
Kashi 32 cikin 100 sun amince da irin wannan aikin.
Binciken ya nuna karin goyon baya ga zaben tsohon Gwamna Deval Patrick, tare da kashi 38 cikin dari na goyon bayan yiwuwar yin takara da kashi 48 cikin dari na adawa da shi.
Sauran sunayen manyan 'yan Democrat da aka tattauna game da yiwuwar tsayawa takara a shekarar 2020 sun haɗa da tsohon mataimakin shugaban Amurka Joe Biden da Sanata na Vermont Bernie Sanders.
