Jakadan Amurka ya zargi kasar Sin da "tabbatarwa" da "tallan farfaganda"
Wata mako bayan wata jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wani sanarwa mai shafuka hudu a cikin jaridar Amurka da ke nuna amfanin cinikin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a kasar Sin ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka wajen yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump a ranar Laraba ta gabata ya yi nuni ga takardar da jaridar China Daily ta biya a cikin Des Moines Register - jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a jihar Iowa - bayan ya zargi China da neman tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka na 6 ga Nuwamba, zargin da China ta musanta.
