Wanda ya kirkiro World Wide Web yana shirin fara sabon Intanet don ɗaukar Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro World Wide Web, yana kaddamar da wani shiri wanda ke neman yin gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin da ya fi dacewa da fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne wanda ya gina daga dandalin Berners-Lee na tushen budewa Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda ake adana bayanan su da kuma abin da mutane ke da izinin samun damar zuwa wane bayani.
A cikin wata hira ta musamman da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi dariya cewa manufar bayan Inrupt ita ce "mulkin duniya".
"Dole ne mu yi shi yanzu", ya ce game da farawa.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don ba mutane damar ƙirƙirar nasu "shagon ajiyar bayanan kan layi" ko POD.
Zai iya ƙunsar jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin ayyukan yi, kalandar, ɗakin karatu na kiɗa da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna samuwa a cikin mai bincike guda daya kuma duk a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke da ban sha'awa game da kantin sayar da bayanan sirri na kan layi shi ne cewa ya dogara ne da mai amfani wanda zai iya samun dama ga irin bayanin.
Kamfanin ya kira shi "karfafawa ta sirri ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar Inrupt, a cewar Shugaba na kamfanin John Bruce, shine kamfanin ya kawo albarkatu, tsari da ƙwarewar da ta dace don taimakawa wajen samar da Solid ga kowa.
A halin yanzu kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu haɓaka da aka yi wa kwangila don aiki a kan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen shirye-shirye masu son rai.
Daga wannan makon, masu bunkasa fasaha a duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen su na musamman ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke samuwa a shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba sa magana da "Facebook da Google game da ko za su gabatar da cikakken canji inda dukkanin tsarin kasuwancin su ke cike da damuwa a cikin dare.
"Ba mu tambayar izinin su".
A cikin wani rubutu a kan Medium da aka buga a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa Inrupt "aikinsa shine samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu don taimakawa kare mutunci da ingancin sabon yanar gizo da aka gina akan Solid".
A 1994, Berners-Lee ya canza Intanet lokacin da ya kafa World Wide Web Consortium a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance murya mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Ko da yake ƙaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance Wanda ya kafa kuma ya kasance Daraktan World Wide Web Consortium, Web Foundation da Open Data Institute.
"Ina da kyakkyawan fata ga wannan zamani na yanar gizo", Berners-Lee ya kara da cewa.
