Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da tsunami da suka afkawa birnin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, jami'an sun ce, tare da adadin wadanda suka mutu ana sa ran su karu.
Da yake an katse sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su samu wani bayani daga yankin Donggala ba, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palu wanda ke kusa da tsakiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5.
A birnin Palu, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya ne, wanda ke kusa da ƙarshen wani ɗan gajeren bay a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da kimanin mutane 379,800 a cikin 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwarsa lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku.
Donggala wani yanki ne wanda ya shimfiɗa sama da kilomita 300 (180 mil) na gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Yankin, yanki ne na gudanarwa a ƙarƙashin lardin, yana da kimanin mutane 299,200 a cikin 2017.
Fishing da noma sune tushen tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, musamman yankin bakin teku na Donggala.
Har ila yau, hakar nickel tana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma galibi an mai da hankali ne a Morowali, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
A cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, tsunami ya yi wa Palu da Donggala yawa, in ji Hukumar Kula da Rashin Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a birnin Donggala.
Har ila yau, tsunami ya afkawa yammacin Donggala a shekara ta 1996, ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana kan yankin Pacific Ring of Fire kuma ana samun girgizar ƙasa a kai a kai.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Wani babban girgizar kasa a yammacin tekun lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba ya haifar da tsunami wanda ya buge kasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: A ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu, girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa gabar yamma ta Sumatra.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, a gabashin Sumatra.
2006: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai girman 6.8 ya afku a kudancin Java, tsibirin da aka fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ya jawo tsunami wanda ya afku a gabar kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: An yi girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.6 a kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
An kashe mutane fiye da 1,100.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa daya daga cikin tsibirin Mentawai, a gabashin Sumatra, ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da dama kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Girgizar ƙasa mai zurfi ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya a Aceh, ta haifar da lalacewa da firgici yayin da mutane suka tuna da halakar da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 2004.
A wannan lokacin, babu tsunami da ya faru, amma gine-gine da suka rushe sun kashe fiye da 100.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai girma ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na yawon buɗe ido na Indonesia, inda ya kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ƙasa ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon buɗe ido a cikin ruwa na ɗan lokaci.
An Kama Ɗan Sara Palin da Laifin Yin Zunubi a Iyali
