Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya suna neman hukuncin kisa ga wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York
Masu gabatar da kara a New York na neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas -- hukuncin kisa mai wuya wanda ba a yi ba a jihar don aikata laifi na tarayya tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekara 30, an ce ya yi amfani da motar hayar Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanyar keke a kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, yana kashe masu tafiya da kuma mai hawa keke a hanyarsa a ranar Oct.
Don a yi wa hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su tabbatar da cewa Saipov "da gangan" ya kashe wadanda aka kashe takwas kuma "da gangan" ya yi mummunan rauni, a cewar sanarwar niyyar neman hukuncin kisa, da aka shigar a Kudancin Gundumar New York.
Dukkanin waɗannan zarge-zargen sun kai ga hukuncin kisa, bisa ga takardar kotu.
Makonni bayan harin, babban juri na tarayya ya yi wa Saipov hukunci mai lamba 22, wanda ya hada da tuhuma takwas na kisan kai don taimakawa cin hanci da rashawa, wanda yawanci masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da shi a cikin shari'o'in aikata laifuka, da kuma tuhumar tashin hankali da lalata motocin mota.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci "shirya da kuma yin shiri sosai", kuma sun bayyana yadda Saipov ya kai harin a matsayin "m, da mugunta da lalata".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi rauni, ya yi rauni, kuma ya rasa iyalan da abokai Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", sanarwa ta niyya ta ce.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekara goma kenan da kotun kudancin New York ta fara tuhumar wani mutum da ake zargi da hukuncin kisa.
An yanke wa wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, hukuncin kisa kan masu sayar da miyagun ƙwayoyi biyu amma a ƙarshe an yanke masa hukuncin rai da rai a kurkuku a watan Satumba na 2009.
A karo na karshe da aka yanke hukuncin kisa a wani shari'ar tarayya a New York a shekara ta 1953 ne ga Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa bisa laifin yin leken asiri ga Tarayyar Soviet a lokacin Yakin Cold shekaru biyu da suka wuce.
An kashe Rosenberg biyu ta wurin kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, dan asalin Uzbekistan, ya nuna rashin nadama a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun kotu.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya gaya wa masu bincike cewa yana jin daɗin abin da ya yi.
Saipov ya shaidawa hukumomi cewa ya yi wahayi zuwa kai harin ne bayan ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa, a cewar zargin.
Ya kuma nemi a nuna tutar ISIS a dakin asibitin sa, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya amince da laifinsa a kan zargin da aka yi masa da mutane 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin masu kare jama'a na tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce "a bayyane yake sun yi takaici" da hukuncin da kotu ta yanke.
"Muna ganin cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karɓar ɗaurin rai a kurkuku ba tare da yiwuwar sakewa ba zai ƙara ɓata lokaci ga dukan waɗanda suka yi abin da ya faru", in ji Patton.
A baya, ƙungiyar kare hakkin Saipov ta nemi masu gabatar da kara kada su nemi hukuncin kisa.
'Yan majalisar Tory sun ce ya kamata a sanya NIGEL FARAGE a kan alhakin tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin 'karfafa sojojin jama'a' a yau a lokacin zanga-zangar da ya yi a taron Tory.
Tsohon shugaban Ukip ya ce 'yan siyasa dole ne su "ji zafi" daga masu shakka game da kudin Tarayyar Turai - kamar yadda daya daga cikin 'yan majalisa na Theresa May ya ba da shawarar ya kamata ya jagoranci tattaunawar da EU.
Mai goyon bayan jam'iyyar Conservative Peter Bone ya shaida wa taron a Birmingham cewa Birtaniya "za ta kasance a waje" a yanzu idan Mr Farage ya zama sakataren Brexit.
Amma kalubalen da Mrs May ke fuskanta wajen sulhunta matsayinta da aka raba sosai an jaddada shi ne ta hanyar masu goyon bayan Remain Tories shiga wani zanga-zanga daban-daban na Brexit a cikin birni.
Firayim Minista na fama da kiyaye shirin sadaukar da ita na Chequers a kan hanya a cikin hare-haren daga masu Brexit, Remainers da EU.
Allies sun dage cewa za ta ci gaba da kokarin cimma yarjejeniya da Brussels duk da mummunar martani - da kuma tilasta Eurosceptics da Labour su zabi tsakanin ta package da kuma 'm.
Mista Bone ya fada wa taron Leave Means Leave a Solihull cewa yana son 'yi wa Chequers' 'ruwa.
Ya ce ya kamata a sanya Mr Farage a matsayin abokin aiki kuma a ba shi alhakin tattaunawar da Brussels.
Ya ce: 'Da a ce shi ne ya yi mana ja-gora, da mun riga mun fita.
Dan majalisar Wellingborough ya kara da cewa: "Zan tsaya a kan Brexit amma muna bukatar mu jefa Chequers".
Da yake nuna adawarsa ga EU, ya ce: 'Ba mu yi yaƙe-yaƙe na duniya don mu zama masu biyayya ba.
Muna son mu kafa dokoki a ƙasarmu.'
Mista Bone ya ƙi jinin shawarwarin da ke nuna cewa ra'ayin jama'a ya canza tun bayan zaben 2016: "Tunanin cewa mutanen Burtaniya sun canza tunaninsu kuma suna son su kasance ba gaskiya bane".
Tory Brexiteer Andrea Jenkyns ma yana wurin, yana gaya wa manema labarai: 'Ina kawai cewa: Firayim Minista, ku saurari mutane.
'Chequers ba shi da shahara a tsakanin jama'a, 'Yan adawa ba za su zabe shi ba, ba shi da shahara a tsakanin jam'iyyarmu da 'yan jaridarmu waɗanda a zahiri suna yin barazanar tituna kuma suna sa a zaɓe mu a farkon wuri.
Don Allah ka sauke Chequers kuma ka fara sauraro.
A cikin sakon da ta kai ga Mrs May, ta kara da cewa: 'Prime ministocin suna riƙe da aikinsu idan sun cika alkawuran su.'
Mr Farage ya ce dole ne a sa 'yan siyasa su "ji zafi" idan suna gab da cin amanar shawarar da aka yanke a zaben 2016.
Ya ce: "Yanzu batun amana ne tsakanin mu - jama'a - da kuma 'yan siyasa.
"Suna kokarin cin amanar Brexit kuma muna nan a yau don gaya musu 'ba za mu bari ku tsira da yin hakan ba.'
A cikin sakon da ya aika wa taron da ke cikin sha'awarsa ya kara da cewa: 'Ina so ku sa rukunin 'yan siyasarmu, waɗanda ke gab da cin amanar Brexit, su ji zafi.
"Muna tattara sojojin mutanen wannan kasar da suka ba mu nasara a Brexit kuma ba za su huta ba har sai mun zama mai zaman kanta, mai zaman kanta, mai girman kai na Burtaniya".
A halin yanzu, Remainers sun yi tafiya ta Birmingham kafin su gudanar da taron awa biyu a tsakiyar birnin.
Wasu 'yan gwagwarmayar sun yi wa Tories Against Brexit banners bayan kaddamar da kungiyar a karshen mako.
Abokin aikin Labor Lord Adonis ya yi wa 'yan Taron ba'a saboda matsalolin tsaro da suka sha da su tare da app na jam'iyyar yayin da taron ya buɗe.
"Waɗannan mutane ne suka gaya mana cewa za su iya samun tsarin IT da duk fasahar Kanada da ƙari, don iyakar da ba ta da rikici, don cinikayya ta kyauta ba tare da iyaka ba a Ireland", ya kara da cewa.
'Wannan farsa ce mai ban tsoro.
Babu irin wannan abu kamar Brexit mai kyau, "in ji shi.
Warren na shirin yin 'duba mai wuya' a takarar shugaban kasa
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta ce za ta yi "tunanin tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa" bayan zaben watan Nuwamba.
Jaridar Boston Globe ta ruwaito 'yar jam'iyyar Democrat ta Massachusetts ta yi magana game da makomar ta a lokacin da take zama a garin garin da ke yammacin Massachusetts a ranar Asabar.
Warren, mai sukar Shugaba Donald Trump, yana neman sake zabar a watan Nuwamba a kan GOP Rep. Geoff Diehl, wanda ya kasance shugaban Trump na yakin neman zaben Massachusetts na 2016.
Ta kasance a tsakiyar tunanin cewa za ta iya kaiwa Trump hari a shekarar 2020.
Taron da ta yi a ranar Asabar da yamma a Holyoke shi ne taro na 36 da ta yi da masu jefa kuri'a da ke amfani da tsarin majalisa tun lokacin da Trump ya hau mulki.
Wani mai halartar taron ya tambaye ta ko tana shirin yin takara a matsayin shugaban kasa.
Warren ya amsa cewa lokaci ya yi da "mata za su je Washington su gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, kuma hakan ya haɗa da mace a saman".
