Elite League: Dundee Stars 5-3 Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer ya zira kwallaye biyu a kan Giants a Dundee
Dundee Stars sun biya bashin asarar da suka yi a gasar Premier da Belfast Giants ta hanyar lashe wasan 5-3 a Dundee a ranar Asabar.
Giants sun samu nasara ta farko ta biyu ta hanyar hare-hare daga Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun kawo matakin gida kafin Dwyer ya dawo da jagorancin Giants.
Francois Bouchard ya daidaita don Dundee kafin Luka Lundvald Nielsen ya zira kwallo biyu ya tabbatar da nasarar su.
Wannan shi ne karo na uku da aka yi a gasar Elite League a kakar wasa ga 'yan Adam Keefe, wadanda suka zo daga baya don doke Dundee 2-1 a Belfast a ranar Juma'a da dare.
