Dwyer ya fara a minti na hudu a 3:35 daga taimakon Kendall McFaull, tare da David Rutherford ya ba da taimako yayin da Beauvillier ya ninka jagorancin minti hudu bayan haka.
A lokacin da aka fara budewa, Sullivan ya dawo da gida a wasan a 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya zama mai samar da Cownie ta daidaitawa a 15:16.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da cewa Giants sun dauki jagorancin farko lokacin da ya buga burinsa na biyu na dare a ƙarshen zangon farko.
Gidan gida ya sake rukuni kuma Bouchard ya sake sanya su a kan daidaituwa tare da burin wasan iko a 27:37.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun haɗu don taimakawa Nielsen ya ba Dundee jagora a karon farko a wasan a ƙarshen lokacin na biyu kuma ya tabbatar da nasarar tare da ƙungiyarsa ta biyar a tsakiyar rabin lokacin ƙarshe.
Giants, da suka rasa hudu daga cikin wasanni biyar da suka yi, suna gida ne ga Milton Keynes a wasan su na gaba a ranar Juma'a.
Mai Kula da Jirgin Sama Ya Mutu Don Tabbatar da Daruruwan Mutane a Jirgin Za Su Iya Tserewa Daga Girgizar Kasa
An yaba wa wani mai kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama a Indonesia a matsayin jarumi bayan ya mutu yana tabbatar da cewa jirgin da ke dauke da daruruwan mutane ya tashi lafiya daga ƙasa.
Mutane sama da 800 sun mutu kuma da yawa sun bace bayan wata babbar girgizar kasa ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi a ranar Juma'a, ta haifar da tsunami.
Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta ci gaba da addabar yankin kuma mutane da yawa suna cikin kwari a birnin Palu.
Amma duk da cewa abokan aikinsa suna gudu don ceton rayukansu, ɗan shekara 21 mai suna Anthonius Gunawan Agung ya ki barin matsayinsa a cikin hasumiyar kula da ke yawo a filin jirgin saman Mutiara Sis Al Jufri a filin jirgin saman Palu.
Ya zauna a wurin don ya tabbata cewa jirgin sama na Batik Air 6321, wanda ke kan hanyar tashi a lokacin, zai iya tashi lafiya.
Sai ya tsallake daga hasumiyar kula da zirga-zirga sa'ad da ya yi tunanin za ta rushe.
Ya mutu daga baya a asibiti.
Kakakin hukumar kula da jiragen sama ta Indonesia, Yohannes Sirait, ya ce wannan matakin na iya ceton daruruwan rayuka, in ji jaridar ABC News ta Ostiraliya.
Mun shirya jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu daga Balikpapan a Kalimantan don mu kai shi wani babban asibiti a wani birni.
Abin takaici mun rasa shi a safiyar yau kafin jirgin ya isa Palu.
Ya daɗa cewa: "Muna baƙin ciki sosai sa'ad da muka ji haka.
A halin yanzu, hukumomi na tsoron cewa adadin wadanda suka mutu zai iya kai dubbai tare da hukumar rage bala'i ta kasar ta ce samun damar zuwa garuruwan Donggala, Sigi da Boutong yana da iyaka.
"Ana ganin cewa har yanzu ana kara yawan mutanen da suka mutu tun da akwai gawawwakin da yawa a ƙarƙashin abin da ya rushe yayin da ba a iya kaiwa ga mutane da yawa ba", in ji kakakin hukumar Sutopo Purwo Nugroho.
Ruwa mai tsawo har zuwa mita shida ya lalata Palu wanda zai gudanar da jana'izar jama'a a ranar Lahadi.
Jiragen sama na soja da na kasuwanci suna kawo taimako da kayayyaki.
Wata mahaifiyar shekara 35 mai suna Risa Kusuma ta gaya wa Sky News: "Kowace minti ɗaya motar asibiti tana kawo gawawwakin mutane.
Ruwa mai tsabta yana da ƙaranci.
Ana fashi da ƙananan kasuwanni a ko'ina".
Jan Gelfand, shugaban kungiyar Red Cross ta kasa da kasa a Indonesia, ya shaida wa CNN: "Kungiyar Red Cross ta Indonesia tana neman taimakon wadanda suka tsira amma ba mu san abin da za su samu ba.
Wannan abin bala'i ne, amma zai iya ƙara muni".
Shugaban Indonesia Joko Widodo ya isa Palu a ranar Lahadi kuma ya gaya wa sojojin kasar: "Ina rokon ku duka ku yi aiki dare da rana don kammala duk wani aiki da ya shafi kwashewar.
Shin kun shirya?"
A farkon wannan shekara, girgizar ƙasa ta addabi ƙasar Indonesia a Lombok kuma ta kashe mutane fiye da 550.
Jirgin sama na Micronesia ya fadi: Kamfanin Air Niugini ya ce mutum daya ya bace bayan hatsarin jirgin sama a tafkin
Kamfanin jirgin sama da ke kula da jirgin da ya fadi a wani tafkin Pacific a Micronesia yanzu ya ce mutum daya ya bace, bayan da ya ce a baya dukkan fasinjoji 47 da ma'aikatan jirgin sun kwashe jirgin da ke nutsewa lafiya.
Kamfanin Air Niugini ya ce a cikin sanarwar cewa tun daga ranar Asabar da yamma, ba ta iya lissafin wani namiji mai tafiya ba.
Kamfanin ya ce yana aiki tare da hukumomin gida, asibitoci da masu bincike don kokarin gano mutumin.
Kamfanin jirgin sama bai amsa ba nan da nan ga buƙatun ƙarin bayani game da fasinjan, kamar shekarunsa ko ƙasarsa.
Jiragen ruwa na gida sun taimaka wajen ceton sauran fasinjoji da ma'aikatan jirgin bayan jirgin ya fadi cikin ruwa yayin da yake kokarin sauka a filin jirgin saman Tsibirin Chuuk.
Jami'ai sun ce a ranar Juma'a an kai mutane bakwai asibiti.
Kamfanin ya ce fasinjoji shida sun kasance a asibiti a ranar Asabar, kuma dukansu suna cikin kwanciyar hankali.
Ba a san ainihin abin da ya sa aka yi hatsarin ba.
Kamfanin jirgin sama da Rundunar Sojin Amurka sun ce jirgin ya sauka a cikin lagoon kusa da hanyar tashi.
Wasu shaidu sun yi tunanin jirgin ya wuce hanyar tashi.
Wani matafiyin Amurka, Bill Jaynes ya ce jirgin ya zo da kasa sosai.
"Wannan abu ne mai kyau", in ji Jaynes.
Jaynes ya ce shi da wasu sun yi nasarar shiga cikin ruwa mai zurfi zuwa ga fitowar gaggawa a jirgin da ke nutsewa.
Ya ce ma'aikatan jirgin sun firgita kuma suna ihu, kuma ya ji rauni a kai.
Rundunar sojin ruwan Amurka ta ce ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa da ke aiki a kusa da wurin don gyara tashar jiragen ruwa sun taimaka wajen ceto ta wajen amfani da jirgin ruwa mai ɗagawa don kawo mutane zuwa gabar teku kafin jirgin ya nutse a cikin ruwa mai mita 30.
Bayanai daga Cibiyar Tsaro ta Sufuri sun nuna cewa mutane 111 sun mutu a hatsarin kamfanonin jiragen sama da aka yi rajista a PNG a cikin shekaru ashirin da suka gabata amma babu wanda ya shafi Air Niugini.
Mai bincike ya bayyana lokacin da aka kone matar da rai
Masu gabatar da kara sun dakatar da shari'arsu a ranar Asabar a sake shari'ar wani mutum wanda ake zargi da kona mace a Mississippi a raye a shekarar 2014.
