Yadda yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China zai iya amfanar Beijing
Kungiyar ta ce, an fara yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China da makamai masu yawa, kuma ko da yake yakin bai ƙare ba, wata matsala tsakanin kasashen na iya zama da amfani ga Beijing a cikin dogon lokaci, masana sun ce.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi gargadi na farko a farkon wannan shekarar ta hanyar sanya haraji kan manyan kayayyakin fitarwa na kasar Sin da suka hada da bangarorin hasken rana, karfe da aluminum.
Mafi girman tashin hankali ya faru a wannan makon tare da sabon haraji da ya shafi kayayyaki masu darajar dala biliyan 200, wanda a zahiri ya sanya rabin duk kayayyakin da ke shigowa Amurka daga China haraji.
Beijing ta yi musu rashawa a kowane lokaci, a kwanan nan ta yi amfani da kudade na kashi biyar zuwa goma bisa dari a kan kayayyakin Amirka da suka kai dala biliyan 60.
Kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin yin daidai da Amurka, kuma tattalin arzikin duniya na biyu ba zai iya yin ido ba.
Sa Washington ta janye tana nufin ta yi biyayya ga bukatun, amma ta yi biyayya ga Amurka a fili zai zama abin kunya ga Shugaba Xi Jinping na kasar Sin.
Duk da haka, masana sun ce idan Beijing ta yi nasara, matsin lamba na yakin cinikayya na Amurka zai iya tallafawa kasar Sin a cikin dogon lokaci ta hanyar rage dogaro tsakanin tattalin arzikin biyu.
Abigail Grace, wata mai bincike da ke nazari a kan Asiya a Cibiyar Tsaro ta Amirka ta ce: "Gaskiyar cewa wani gaggawa da aka yanke a kan batun siyasa a Washington ko kuma Beijing zai iya haifar da yanayin da zai sa tattalin arziki ya soma raguwa a kowace ƙasa, a gaskiya ya fi haɗari fiye da yadda masu kallo suka sani a dā.
Syria 'ta shirye' don 'yan gudun hijira su koma, in ji Ministan Harkokin Wajen
Syria ta ce ta shirya don dawowar 'yan gudun hijira da son rai kuma tana neman taimako wajen sake gina kasar da ta lalace sakamakon yaki na tsawon shekaru bakwai.
Da yake jawabi a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan Harkokin Wajen kasar Walid al-Moualem ya ce yanayin kasar na inganta.
"A yau halin da ake ciki a kan ƙasa ya fi kwanciyar hankali da kwanciyar hankali godiya ga ci gaba da aka samu a yaki da ta'addanci", in ji shi.
Gwamnati na ci gaba da gyara yankunan da 'yan ta'adda suka hallaka domin dawo da al'ada.
Yanzu akwai dukkan yanayi don dawowar 'yan gudun hijira da yardar rai zuwa kasar da suka bar saboda ta'addanci da kuma matakan tattalin arziki na gefe guda da suka shafi rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum da kuma rayuwarsu.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa fiye da 'yan Siriya miliyan 5.5 sun bar kasar tun lokacin da yakin ya fara a shekarar 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida da ke zaune a kasar suna bukatar taimakon agaji.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Syria za ta yi maraba da taimakon da za a yi wajen sake gina kasar da aka hallaka.
Amma ya jaddada cewa ba za ta yarda da taimakon da ake bukata ko kuma taimako daga kasashen da suka tallafa wa 'yan tawaye ba.
Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a birnin Paris
Team Turai ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder ta 2018 ta doke Team USA ta hanyar ci gaba da ci 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Golf National a waje da Paris, Faransa.
Amurka ta rasa sau shida a jere a ƙasar Turai kuma ba ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake samun kambin yayin da tawagar dan Denmark Thomas Bjorn ta kai maki 14.5 da suke bukata don doke Amurka.
Tauraron Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya yi gwagwarmaya a mafi yawan gasar, ya jefa wasan sa cikin ruwa a rami na 16 na par-3, ya ba da wasansa ga Francesco Molinari.
Mai wasan golf na Italiya Molinari ya haskaka a duk zagaye, ya zama 1 daga cikin 'yan wasa 4 da suka taɓa zuwa 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara tsarin gasar a shekarar 1979.
Dan Amurka Jordan Spieth ya tashi 5 & 4 da dan wasan da ya fi ƙasa a cikin tawagar Turai, Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark.
Mafi kyawun dan wasan duniya, Dustin Johnson, ya fadi 2 da 1 ga Ian Poulter na Ingila wanda zai iya buga wasan Ryder Cup na karshe.
Tsohon tsohon dan wasan Spain Sergio Garcia wanda ya lashe gasar Ryder Cup guda takwas ya zama dan Turai mafi nasara a duk lokacin gasar tare da maki 25.5 a cikin aikinsa.
"Ba na yawan kuka amma yau ba zan iya yin hakan ba.
Shekara ce mai wuya.
Ina godiya sosai ga Thomas da ya zaɓe ni kuma ya gaskata da ni.
Ina farin ciki, ina farin ciki da samun kofin.
Yana da game da tawagar, kuma ina farin ciki na iya taimakawa, "in ji Garcia mai motsin rai bayan nasarar Turai.
Ya mika wutar ga ɗan ƙasarsa John Ram wanda ya kashe almara na golf na Amurka Tiger Woods 2 & 1 a wasan guda a ranar Lahadi.
Rahm mai shekara 23 ya ce: "Na yi alfahari sosai da na yi nasara a kan Tiger Woods, na yi girma ina kallon wannan mutumin.
Woods ya rasa dukkan wasanni hudu da ya buga a Faransa kuma yanzu yana da rikodin rikodin 13-21-3 na Ryder Cup.
Wani kididdiga mai ban mamaki daga daya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasa na dukan lokaci, da ya lashe 14 manyan lakabi na biyu kawai Jack Nicklaus.
Team USA ta yi gwagwarmaya a duk karshen mako don nemo fairways sai dai Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Finau, wadanda suka buga golf mai girma a duk lokacin gasar.
Kyaftin na Amurka Jim Furyk ya yi magana bayan wasan da ya takaici ga tawagarsa, "Ina alfahari da wadannan mutane, sun yi gwagwarmaya.
Akwai lokacin da muka yi amfani da wannan safiya wajen yin amfani da Turai.
Mun yi watsi da shi.
Ka ɗauki hatsa zuwa ga Thomas.
Shi babban kyaftin ne.
Duk 'yan wasansa 12 sun yi wasa sosai.
Za mu sake rukuni, zan yi aiki tare da PGA na Amurka da kuma Kwamitin Ryder Cup kuma za mu ci gaba.
Ina son waɗannan mutane 12 kuma ina alfahari da zama kyaftin.
Dole ne ka juya ka hat.
Mun yi nasara".
Red Tide Update: Rashin taro a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Rahoton da aka samu daga Hukumar Kifi da Tsuntsaye ta Florida ya nuna cewa yawan Red Tide ya ragu a wasu sassan yankin Tampa Bay.
A cewar FWC, ana samun rahotanni game da yanayin fure a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier counties - wanda ke nuna raguwar taro.
Fure mai launin ruwan kasa mai launin ruwan kasa ya shimfiɗa kimanin mil 130 na gabar teku daga arewacin Pinellas zuwa kudancin lardin Lee.
Ana iya samun kayan kwalliya kimanin mil 10 a gabar tekun gundumar Hillsborough, amma a wurare kadan idan aka kwatanta da makon da ya gabata.
An kuma lura da Red Tide a cikin gundumar Pasco.
An ba da rahoton matsakaitan taro a cikin ko a cikin yankin Pinellas County a makon da ya gabata, ƙananan zuwa manyan taro a cikin yankin Hillsborough County, bayanan da ke cikin manyan taro a cikin Manatee County, bayanan da ke cikin ko a cikin yankin Sarasota County, bayanan da ke cikin tsakiyar taro a cikin Charlotte County, bayanan da ke cikin ko a cikin yankin Lee County, da ƙananan taro a cikin County Collier.
Ana ci gaba da samun cututtukan numfashi a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da kuma Colier.
Ba a samu wani tashin hankali a cikin numfashi a arewa maso yammacin Florida a makon da ya gabata ba.
